# Git Push/Pull Convention (DEPRECATED)

> **This rule is deprecated.** The `ai-platform-webui` repository has been replaced by `ai-platform-strategy`, which uses standard `dev` branch workflows identical to all other managed repos. No special push/pull routing is required.

## Current Convention (all repos)

All 5 managed repositories use standard git push/pull:

```bash
git push origin HEAD         # push current branch
git pull origin dev          # pull from dev
```

## PR Creation

```bash
gh pr create --base dev ...
```

## History

Previously, `ai-platform-webui` required pushing to a remote `tmp` branch (`git push origin HEAD:tmp`). This exception was removed when the project migrated to `ai-platform-strategy` with full dev-branch workflow.
